snippet.title: Supurr Cat Cafe: Sandwich Rush - Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist the game on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2658690?utm_source=youtube&utm_campaign=trailer

Stack towering sandwiches with the help of cute cat friends while building up your dream cat cafe. With plenty of hungry quirky customers around, you’ll need to upgrade your cafe, find new cats to help you and up your sandwich game to keep them happy!

We are a team of 2 passionate indie devs and we can't wait to have you join us and build your own Supurr Cat Cafe!
